org.spongepowered.api.data.manipulators.items

Interface StoredEnchantmentData

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<StoredEnchantmentData>, DataManipulator<StoredEnchantmentData>, DataSerializable, MappedData<Enchantment,Integer,StoredEnchantmentData>

    public interface StoredEnchantmentData
extends MappedData<Enchantment,Integer,StoredEnchantmentData>
    Represents stored enchantments that can be used to apply the stored Enchantments on to another item stack.

    Common uses of StoredEnchantmentData is with enchanted books and anvils.
